🌟NEW COCONUT CARAMEL COOKIE CUP!🥥🍪

We’re so excited to introduce you to our new Coconut Caramel Cookie Cup - AKA your new chocolate obsession!💥

Dive into a rich 58% cacao organic dark milk chocolate shell filled with dreamy coconut butter, blended with toasted coconut flakes, a hint of white chocolate, a dash of smoked sea salt, and topped with crunchy graham cracker magic.✨

And the best part? It only has 5g of sugar per cup!

Keep your eyes and taste buds ready! 👀
